snippet.title: Etredal
snippet.description:
Learn how to use Unity to make great games on this channel and watch some of my showcase videos about what I'm working on!  From visual scripting tools, to game development decisions, and useful assets/packages, you can learn a lot on this channel.  Some series that I have worked on teach you how to implement AI in your game, and I have my Chess Tutorial Series!

etredal@gmail.com
